<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="9" type="multiple">
<paragraph blockId="8.[227,1436,357,456]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Family and genus characters: five-segmented maxillary palps with second segment longest; threesegmented labial palps; forewing forks II, III, and V and hindwing forks I, III, and V present; tibial spurs 2/2/4.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
